  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can 100 Men Defeat a Gorilla?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the battlefield and become part of the most absurd and epic debate the internet has ever seen! Take control of 100 men in a brutal one-on-one fight against the most pissed-off gorilla you’ve ever faced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hit matters. Every move counts.<br>Will you coordinate attacks, chain combos, and push your squad to their limits to take down the beast?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦍 <strong>Action-Packed Combat</strong>: Punch, dodge, and combo your way through the fight in a chaotic yet strategic brawl.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 <strong>100 Fighters, One Goal</strong>: Use your men wisely — it's not just brute force, it's about timing and precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Create Your Fighter</strong>: Customize your warrior with unique styles, outfits, and flair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔓 <strong>Unlockable Modes</strong>: Discover new ways to play, crazy challenges, and even more chaotic battles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to laugh, rage, and get hooked by this ridiculous — yet strangely compelling — showdown.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can 100 Men Defeat a Gorilla?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the battlefield and become part of the most absurd and epic debate the internet has ever seen! Take control of 100 men in a brutal one-on-one fight against the most pissed-off gorilla you’ve ever faced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hit matters. Every move counts.<br>Will you coordinate attacks, chain combos, and push your squad to their limits to take down the beast?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦍 <strong>Action-Packed Combat</strong>: Punch, dodge, and combo your way through the fight in a chaotic yet strategic brawl.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 <strong>100 Fighters, One Goal</strong>: Use your men wisely — it's not just brute force, it's about timing and precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Create Your Fighter</strong>: Customize your warrior with unique styles, outfits, and flair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔓 <strong>Unlockable Modes</strong>: Discover new ways to play, crazy challenges, and even more chaotic battles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to laugh, rage, and get hooked by this ridiculous — yet strangely compelling — showdown.</p>",
